The,BillForward,API,integrates,billing,into,web,services,It,is,available,in,REST,architecture,with,JSON,methods,and,OAuth,as,the,authentication,method,Endpoints,for,sandbox,and,production,are,part,of,the,resources,along,with,SDKs,HTTP,requests,documentation,and,URL,addresses,Enterprises,can,use,the,API,to,unify,billing,through,product,market,and,departmental,alternatives